webpackJsonp([0x5c6818ebd33f],{7653:function(e,a){e.exports={data:{post:{html:'<p><a href="http://www.scandinavian-park.com/index.php?id=10"><img src="http://www.papascott.de/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2006/07/scandinavian_park_flyer.jpg" alt="scandinavian_park_flyer" /></a></p>\n<p>We took a trip up north to Denmark for the weekend, and I was most impressed by our stop Sunday morning at <a href="http://www.scandinavian-park.com/index.php?id=10">Scandinavian Park</a> in Flensburg, a shopping center for Danes just inside Germany with a business plan based entirely on selling Danish beer at German prices. Prices are prominently displayed in Danish Kroner, and it\'s open <a href="http://www.scandinavian-park.com/index.php?id=33">late evenings and Sundays</a>. Among other shops there\'s a cheap <a href="http://www.etaphotel.com/etaphotel/fichehotel/gb/etp/6299/fiche_hotel.shtml">Etap hotel</a>, a <a href="http://www.heingericke-flensburg.de/">motorcycle supply shop</a>, a <a href="http://www.hier-bin-ich-koenig.de/">slot-machine arcade</a>, and a <a href="http://www.beate-uhse.com/">Beate Uhse</a> sex shop. One stop shopping at its finest.</p>\n<p>Of course if the EU ever equalized alcohol taxes the whole concept would be bankrupt in an instant.</p>',fields:{title:"Scandinavian Park",date:"24 Jul 2006",url:"https://papascott.de/2006-07-24-scandinavian-park/"}}},pathContext:{slug:"/2006-07-24-scandinavian-park/",prev:{fields:{title:"Let's go exploring!",date:"24 Jul 2006",slug:"/2006-07-24-lets-go-exploring/"}},next:{fields:{title:"Second Whiney Expat Bloggers in Germany Meet Up",date:"24 Jul 2006",slug:"/2006-07-24-second-whiney-expat-bloggers-in-germany-meet-up/"}}}}}});
//# sourceMappingURL=path---2006-07-24-scandinavian-park-0167dcc0684dc39ff32b.js.map